1)tokenize  2)stopwords  3)ngram  4)stem  5)WSD
nltk.tokenize always has to components main as word_tokenize and sent_tokenize
nltk.corpus has stopwords function to get a ist of stopwords and string has a list of punctuations
nlk.colloctions has multiple ngram functions like bigram, trigram ,quadgram etc
nltk.stem has LancasterStemmer function for stemming
nltk.corpus has wordnet function for meaning and context also nltk.wsd has lesk function for contextual meaning of word in the sentence
